          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Since I touched You, I don’t care—"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "For I’ve found You’re the only life worth living."
